      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward transportation with plenty of life left for the right buyer. This vehicle shows its age cosmetically, but it offers solid everyday utility and a chance to get on the road without stretching your budget. A practical choice for commuting, a first car, or a backup vehicle\u2014priced to sell and backed by a transparent, no-nonsense presentation.",
