      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great for someone handy, a first-time buyer on a tight budget, or anyone wanting affordable wheels without spending a fortune. Priced fairly and listed by someone who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with.",
      "price": 7950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong value for someone wanting an affordable driver or weekend project. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it has a solid, mechanical feel and offers dependable basic transportation with plenty of life left for the next owner who doesn\u2019t mind a rough-around-the-edges example. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis remains usable, and it\u2019s a great candidate for a tidy-up, commuter duty, or parts-saving enthusiast ownership. If you\u2019re looking for inexpensive entry into ownership with real upside, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap. Running. Gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. Great budget beater or project.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of road-worn character you notice right away\u2014an honest driver with a story in every panel and plenty of life left for someone who appreciates potential. It\u2019s a great fit for a hands-on owner, a budget commuter, or anyone looking for an inexpensive set of wheels with personality and purpose. If you enjoy turning a practical buy into something you can truly make your own, this one offers a compelling starting point at a wallet-friendly price.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
