      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a practical choice for a buyer seeking straightforward value, everyday utility, and a low cost of entry. An excellent opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing inexpensive wheels without overpaying.",
      "price": 4900.0,
